{% extends "www/_layouts/layout-left-pane.njk" %}
{% set pageTitle = "Buttons" %}

{% block content %}
<p>
  <strong>Buttons</strong> and <strong>links</strong> are items used to perform an action on a
  page
</p>
<p>
  It's important to know when to use a <strong>button</strong> or went to use a
  <strong>
    <a href="/components/links/">link</a>
  </strong>
</p>
<p>
  <strong>Buttons</strong> should be used in situations where a user might need to preform an
  action, such as:
</p>
<ul>
  <li>Submitting a form</li>
  <li>Uploading</li>
  <li>Specify a next or previous step in a process</li>
  <li>Begin a new task</li>
</ul>

